newsitem.title: TURKEY: SOCCER-FENERBAHCE V MANCHESTER UNITED TEAMS.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-FENERBAHCE V MANCHESTER UNITED TEAMS.

text.p: Teams for Wednesday's European Cup Champions' League Group C match between Fenerbahce of Turkey and Manchester United of England:

Fenerbahce - 1-Rustu Recber; 2-Ilker Yagcioglu, 3-Uche Okechukwu, 4-Jes Hogh, 5-Kemalettin Senturk, 6-Halil Ibrahim Kara, 8-Tuncay Akgun, 9-Elvir Bolic, 10-Augustine "Jay Jay" Okacka, 11-Emil Kostadinov, 16-Bulent Uygun

Manchester United - 1-Peter Schmeichel, 2-Gary Neville, 3-Denis Irwin, 4-David May, 5-Ronny Johnsen, 6-Gary Pallister, 7-Eric Cantona, 8-Nicky Butt, 10-David Beckham, 14-Jordi Cruyff, 20-Ole Solskjaer
